<emphasis box="[307,551,1274,1297]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Exallococcus laureliae</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Miller, D. R. &amp; Gonzalez, R. H." box="[558,930,1274,1297]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="131 - 163" refId="ref51269" refString="Miller, D. R. &amp; Gonzalez, R. H. (1975). A taxonomic analysis of the Eriococcidae of Chile. Revista Chilena de Entomologia, 9, 131 - 163." type="journal article" year="1975">Miller &amp; González 1975: 150–152</bibRefCitation>
